"4\bLuddite Rule (\ior, George Lucas Rule\i)\b\n
"jSpeaking of which, technology is inherently evil and is the exclusive province of the Bad Guys. They're the ones with the robots, factories, cyberpunk megalopolises and floating battle stations, while the Good Guys live in small villages in peaceful harmony with nature. (\iAlthough somehow your guns and/or heavily armed airships are exempted from this.\i)\n\n
