"=\b"Silly Squall, bringing a sword to a gunfight..."\b\n
"‚No matter what timeframe the game is set in -- past, present, or future -- the main hero and his antagonist will both use a sword for a weapon. (\iTherefore, you can identify your antagonist pretty easily right from the start of the game just by looking for the other guy who uses a sword.\i) These swords will be far more powerful than any gun and often capable of distance attacks.\p
