"9\bO Brother, Where Art Thou? (\iMelfice Rule\i)\b\n
"òIf the male hero has an older sibling, the sibling will also be male and will turn out to be one of the major villains. If the hero has a younger sibling, the sibling will be female and will be kidnapped and held hostage by the villains.\n\n
