"\bThousand Year Rule\b\n
"The Ancient Evil returns to savage the land every thousand years on the dot, and the last time it showed up was just about 999.9875 years ago. Despite their best efforts, heroes of the past were never able to do more than seal the Evil away again for the future to deal with (\iwhich brings up the question of just how exactly does this "sealing away" work anyway, but never mind.\i) The good news is that this time, the Evil will get destroyed permanently. The bad news is that you're the one who's going to have to do it.\n\n
