"-\bPrinciple of Narrative Efficiency\b\n
"If the main villain (\ior the enemy you've been trying to kill for most of the game before he summons the real final villain\i) was ever defeated in the past by another group of adventurers, one of them will secretly be in your party and one of them will be the hero's father.\n\n
