"1\bLast Law of Travel (\iBig Joe Rule\i)\b\n
"RAs has been described, you must endure great trials just to get from town to town: locating different vehicles, operating ancient transport mechanisms, evading military blockades, the list goes on. But that's just you. Every other character in the game seems to have no trouble getting to any place in the world on a moment's notice.\n\n
