"5\b"So, Andross, you reveal your true form!"\b\n
"ùYou will have to kill the evil villain at least twice at the end of the game. First the villain will look like a person or some creature and be rather easy to kill. Then he will grow to about 50 times the hero's size and be much harder to kill.\n\n
